nodes.text: A noblewoman from the planet Alsakan lived during the Cold War between the Galactic Republic and the reconstituted Sith Empire, during which she was part of a proposed marriage alliance with several Mid Rim traders. The alliance would safeguard trade in the Mid Rim for generations, but the noblewoman initially refused to agree to the alliance. A diplomat attempted to reason with the woman, only to discover that she was objecting to the terms of the trade agreement. The diplomat modified the terms of the agreement, impressing both the noble and the traders, and the marriage went ahead as scheduled.
